#
# "For where two or three are gathered together in my name,
#  there am I in the midst of them." â€” Matthew 18:20
#
# alfred-worship assembly â€” One person starts worship, all mesh nodes
# get a notification. Same track and Scripture synchronized across
# machines. The Body of Christ, connected through the mesh.
#
# BUILD: v7.77 Kingdom of God Edition
# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

